title: Miss Wildgame
overview: Wildgame Innovations and Outdoor Sportsman Group are pleased to bring you a brand new series designed to see if these insta-famous huntresses are the real deal or are they just posing to gain social "likes" or "follows". Introducing Miss Wildgame, the first hardcore hunting competition to put these huntresses with massive followings to the test - going head-to-head in an epic whitetail hunting competition!
